Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.02,0:24:30.50,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}全部如愿之后
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.92,0:24:35.60,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}我们还会贪婪地没有休止
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.85,0:24:39.88,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}直到开始后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.01,0:24:42.53,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}永远过不够的昨天
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.53,0:24:44.92,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}和不断积蓄的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.92,0:24:50.64,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}就这样重叠着伴我前行
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.96,0:24:56.85,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}能够成为非常喜欢的人的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.94,0:25:01.92,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}非常喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.02,0:25:07.08,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}连这样的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.22,0:25:11.82,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}我还无法完全相信
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.82,0:25:16.52,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}总是难以如愿
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.68,0:25:22.24,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}多想再长高一些
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.30,0:25:24.62,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}愿我可以笑着
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.69,0:25:27.10,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}用幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.17,0:25:30.34,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}为明天
